reviewText: Kim Possible: The Villain Files is a Disney DVD compilation of four episodes of the classic Disney Channel animated action-comedy series. In this DVD, Kim and her sidekick Ron Stoppable battles against, Dr. Drakken, Shego, and other evil baddies. The special features includes a villian house party game and trailers to other Disney Channel movies on DVD. This Kim Possible DVD is perfect for teens and tweens who are fans of the programme. :)
